      • convertElements

        public static void convertElements(UmlModel umlModel,
                                   CodeRepresentation codeRepresentation,
                                   TemporaryModel tmpModel)
        Static method converting the UmlElements of a given UmlModel to CodeElements for the CodeRepresentation.
        If the UmlModel contains UmlElements at the top level, a CodePackage is created, where the converted CodeElements are added to.
        Parameters:
        umlModel - the UmlModel containing the UmlElements and UmlPackages to be converted
        codeRepresentation - the CodeRepresentation to which the converted elements should be added
        tmpModel - the TemporaryModel containing the maps to add UmlElements and converted CodeElements to

      • convertElement

        public static CodeElement convertElement(UmlElement element,
                                         UmlPackage umlPackage,
                                         CodeParent parent,
                                         TemporaryModel tmpModel)
        Static method to convert a given UmlElement to a CodeElement and adding it to a CodePackage.
        Delegates the conversion of CodeLiterals to the LiteralConverter
        Delegates the conversion of CodeFields to the FieldConverter
        Delegates the conversion of CodeConstructors to the ConstructorConverter
        Delegates the conversion of CodeMethods to the MethodConverter
        Delegates the conversion of CodeTemplateParameters to the TemplateParameterConverter
        Parameters:
        element - the UmlElement to be converted
        umlPackage - the UmlPackage used to get the CodePackage out of the map of the TemporaryModel. Can be null in case of the conversion of a nested UmlElement
        parent - the CodeParent to add the converted CodePackage to. Can be null in which case it needs to be taken out of the map in the TemporaryModel with the UmlPackage as key.
        tmpModel - the TemporaryModel containing the maps to add temporary CodeTemplateBindings and converted CodeTemplateParameters and CodeElements to
        Returns:
        the converted CodeElement
